Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.10,0:01:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片名：Flutter of Birds　第二章　線香花火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.66,0:02:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你這麼悲傷的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美雨會無法放心上天堂的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.78,0:02:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.65,0:02:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要成為優秀的醫生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了美雨我一定要成為好醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才對啊　裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太像他的個性了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來還擔心他會因為美雨的死而意志消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來他很快就恢復正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他必須這樣才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後他還會經歷很多生離死別的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說等他當醫生以後啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一為了某人之死就無法醫治別的病人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣是無法當醫生的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？原來是指這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還誤以為妳不舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂　森の診療所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈　是妳的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我的？是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是妳的未婚夫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好　來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈的表情很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的　有點令人羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到她已有未婚夫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點意外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作　你沒有女朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.53,0:04:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有　我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.26,0:05:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫科學生是沒時間約會的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少來了　裝模作樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是因為你不受歡迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡哪一類型的女性？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡的是不會嘲弄年紀比她大的醫學生的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.05,0:05:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野妳呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.58,0:05:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳喜歡什麼類型的男性？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎？我喜歡的類型是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡的男人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.36,0:05:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的類型？這是什麼？完全聽不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作你不需要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我再考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.50,0:06:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松井
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才妳還很開心的啊　發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事與你無關　請回去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.18,0:06:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擔心妳的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能回去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你擔心我？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.52,0:06:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然妳是個精明能幹的護士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但妳只是一個普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會有煩惱的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果獨自揹負太多煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.53,0:06:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳會崩潰的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以妳需要找人傾訴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我不是太令人信任
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我可以聽一聽妳的煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松井
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很溫柔　松井
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然平時不太可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.73,0:07:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時你卻有令人信賴的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的　我正在為某事煩惱著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事很難應付　我不知應怎辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你或許可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我找出答案
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你　松井
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不要說　和我做愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？朝比奈　我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.55,0:07:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松井　拜託你給我答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松井　我來幫你做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得這麼硬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈小姐　太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松井　你的越來越大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼舒服嗎？那我就讓你更舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈小姐好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈小姐　妳這麼做　我會…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松井　可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…已經忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松井的東西插到我的下體了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:08:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松井　松井
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松井
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再更激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再更用力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.13,0:09:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松井　我…我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要高潮了　高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.55,0:09:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的未婚夫是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他要求一個結婚條件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我辭掉護士的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是妳若能輕易放棄護士工作的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.33,0:10:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就不會煩惱了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有多熱愛這份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼以此為榮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松井
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跟我說大話了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了　回去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.25,0:10:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在X光片室做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是做健康檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健康檢查？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想檢查時就檢查　這是醫生女兒的特權
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作你要不要也檢查？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好可能出乎意料地找到奇怪的病哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別胡說八道了　那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸　怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題　沒什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.40,0:11:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我回去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不知道對我是什麼想法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼在發呆？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼心事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.87,0:11:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別瞞我　別瞞我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事儘管對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.00,0:11:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是可以傾聽妹妹的煩惱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你就聽聽我的煩惱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:12:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的　我的朋友中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個女生一直暗戀一個男生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那個男生周圍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多優秀的女人和女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那男生對那女生根本就不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是女生卻非常喜歡那男生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是又活潑又健康的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.04,0:12:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是不敢向男生告白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.81,0:12:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作　這應該怎麼做好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛的煩惱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作覺得怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是很瞭解　但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很羨慕那男生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野嗎？門沒關
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣？這和服適合我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常適合妳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…妳是怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何打扮成這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一起去廟會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.01,0:13:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廟會？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚有夏之廟會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來我會打中的　天曉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作　唷囉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.84,0:14:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作　很好玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.81,0:14:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像回到以前一起玩的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要繼續保護著森野的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好哥哥的本份
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.63,0:14:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我還小的時候媽媽就死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡這種煙火了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很短暫　它卻拚命放出光亮的火花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算生命很短暫　卻努力綻放光亮的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳穿制服要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.44,0:15:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在有社團活動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.94,0:15:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社團活動？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傍晚之前我會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.55,0:15:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.01,0:15:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野今天起有社團活動了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.32,0:15:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松井
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天謝謝你　託你的福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到答案了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要繼續當護士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是我的幸福之路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈護士長以後請繼續指教
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.70,0:15:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個當然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會跟以前一樣繼續嚴格指導你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂　森の診療所
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野受傷了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？為什麼這麼急？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷口呢？妳的身體沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.83,0:16:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷口？我只是扭傷足踝罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是扭傷足踝？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才裕作的表情很好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的　別再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算我錯了就是嘛　是我的誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的關心　裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能成為好醫生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題　裕作已經做得很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.88,0:16:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎？我一點實際的感覺也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看診所裡的病人們的表情就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很信任裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.72,0:17:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要急
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作只要盡全力去做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照自己的步調來做就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太勉強可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起　森野　我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的　我很高興　高興極了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作第一次把我當成女人看待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了　回去吧　裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸在家裡一定擔心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:17:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野？妳沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.05,0:18:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心　裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野？森野！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊醫生　快治療森野啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的病和她母親一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.25,0:18:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是遺傳病
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.41,0:18:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以現在的醫療技術是治不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼森野她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.82,0:18:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野竟然得了不治之症
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野　難道我無法為妳做任何事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是為了什麼甘願當醫生的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.05,0:19:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是因為小時候看到妳的媽媽這樣痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野的病遲早會發展到跟她母親一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.36,0:19:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了　我是為了森野而當醫生的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.83,0:19:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了　森野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多等一段時間我就可以治好妳了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.98,0:19:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.51,0:19:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳醒了　森野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.65,0:19:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下　我馬上喊熊醫生來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下　裕作　請留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要裕作留在我的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.73,0:20:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野　妳明明很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻故意掩飾痛苦強顏歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們約定好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽死的時候裕作曾經說過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓媽媽擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.54,0:20:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天起不可以哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要變堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野　妳還一直守著那麼久的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是與裕作的約定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作　求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把現在我說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當成妹妹的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.57,0:20:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請當成是一個女人說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好　我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.74,0:20:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保證
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.91,0:20:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你　裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:20:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.25,0:20:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小時候開始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡的就是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是　森野
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是以哥哥而是男人的身份喜歡妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興　裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.57,0:21:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你　快點讓我成為你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.91,0:21:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我活下去的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.24,0:21:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.76,0:21:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難為情　裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.71,0:22:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作　這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.48,0:22:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會癢的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.45,0:22:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作　那裡不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.53,0:22:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野　妳有快感了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.57,0:22:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.97,0:22:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你看到我這模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.90,0:22:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家不能再當你的妹妹了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.77,0:22:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直期待著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作跟我作愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.71,0:22:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不是裕作的妹妹了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.02,0:22:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.92,0:22:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作　那裡很髒的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.19,0:22:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.60,0:22:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.74,0:22:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.30,0:22:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你　來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.37,0:23:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入我裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.44,0:23:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎？森野
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.41,0:23:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.51,0:23:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.72,0:23:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野　對不起　妳還好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.95,0:23:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事　雖然有點痛可是沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.52,0:23:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是裕作的大棒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.39,0:23:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.23,0:23:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以跟裕作合為一體
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.23,0:23:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野　知道嗎？我要動了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.81,0:23:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以感覺到裕作的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.11,0:23:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作已經充滿在我的體內
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.96,0:23:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.42,0:23:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作　裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.53,0:23:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.75,0:24:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作　我…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.35,0:24:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於從裕作最喜歡的妹妹的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.39,0:24:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升格成最喜歡的女孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.69,0:24:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊　森野
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.69,0:24:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得…能夠…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.56,0:24:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟裕作結合真是太幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.70,0:24:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你　裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.07,0:24:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.67,0:24:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂　森野
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.54,0:24:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野　別走啊　森野
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.11,0:24:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們約定了我一定會治好妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.85,0:24:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳快甦醒啊　森野
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.55,0:24:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.29,0:24:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.53,0:27:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後我成為了醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.53,0:27:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在能夠使你過得更加好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.75,0:27:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作，你回來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.35,0:27:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，今天是美雨的死忌
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.39,0:27:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.69,0:27:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個故事我要告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.69,0:27:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一晚我們做愛的時候，我聽到了美雨的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.56,0:27:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在溫和的陽光中，然後醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.70,0:27:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信美雨還是活在我們周圍
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.07,0:28:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.67,0:28:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會治好你的病的，森野
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.54,0:28:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.11,0:28:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.85,0:28:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.55,0:28:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了，森野
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.29,0:28:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來，裕作
